FBIS4-29270 "dreas116_d_94016" FBIS-EAS-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 South Korea Former Minister Named `Special' Ambassador Former Minister Named `Special' Ambassador SK1606061394 Seoul YONHAP in English 0545 GMT 16 Jun 94 SK1606061394 Seoul YONHAP English BFN [Text] Seoul, June 16 (YONHAP) -- Former Vice Foreign Minister Hong Sun-yong was reinstated to the ministry as special grade one ambassador-at-large Thursday. Hong, who served as ambassador to the former Soviet Union, was replaced last month. He is expected to tour South America as South Korea's special envoy from next month.
